manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "streamcore_youtube_chat_ingest"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "streamcore_youtube_chat_ingest"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1.72"
reqwest = "0.11.18"
serde = "1.0.175"
serde_json = "1.0.81"
streamcore_chat_objects = "0.1.4"
streamcore_message_client = "0.1.3"
tokio-stream = "0.1.6"
warp = "0.3.2"

[dependencies.chromiumoxide]
git = "https://github.com/mattsse/chromiumoxide"
branch = "main"
features = ["tokio-runtime"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.17"
default-features = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.17.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tokio-tungstenite]
version = "0.20.0"
features = ["native-tls"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "0.4"
features = ["serde", "v4"]
